{"_path":"/gists/font","_dir":"gists","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"字体","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"字体"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"字体"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h5","props":{"id":"深入理解line-heightvertical-align"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"link","props":{"type":"h5","to":"https://mgear-file.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%20line-height%E3%80%81vertical-align%20-%20%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A5%E5%BE%80%E5%89%8D%E8%B5%B0_%E4%B8%8D%E5%9B%9E%E5%A4%B4%20-%20%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%AD.html","source":"https://www.cnblogs.com/wfeicherish/p/8884903.html"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"《深入理解：line-height、vertical-align》"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由于每个字体占据的行内的实际高度是要按照字体属性计算的，font-size 指定了 em-square 的大小，但是字体展示在行内的高度（内容区高度）是按照字体的 Ascent 和 Descent 属性计算的，这就是为什么设置了字体的展示范围要比 font-size 大得多。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见下图， font-size 为 100 时，实际的字体展示区域为 $$(Ascent+Descent)*(font-size/em-sqaure)$$"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也就是 $$(1100 + 540) * (100 / 1000) = 164px$$"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"font-size | https://www.pinterest.com/pin/an-introduction-to-the-inline-formatting-context-explores-lineheight-and-verticalalign-properties-as-well-as-the-font-metrics-underst--54958057934130156/","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20210924175812.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以可想而知，line-height 设为数字时，行高为 font-size 的值的倍数关系，是个糟糕的实践。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因为不同字体的属性还不一样，而行盒子计算其自身高度是取每行中个元素的最高点和最低点，这也就导致了行高和字体的高度可能对不上。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"line-box | https://www.pinterest.com/pin/an-introduction-to-the-inline-formatting-context-explores-lineheight-and-verticalalign-properties-as-well-as-the-font-metrics-underst--54958057934130156/","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20210924172252.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"和大家理解的不太一样，line-height：middle 并不是指父元素的中线位置，而是父元素的 base-line + half-x-height。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"免费商用字体"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"免费商用字体"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"![[Pasted image 20230730231610.png]]"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.figma.com/file/mtPPLBBq4p3RFKucX47wFW/%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%95%86%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%BA%93-(Community)?type=design&node-id=1-177&mode=design&t=NBLaDAXojVu6beVl-0","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://www.figma.com/file/mtPPLBBq4p3RFKucX47wFW/%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%95%86%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%BA%93-(Community)?type=design&node-id=1-177&mode=design&t=NBLaDAXojVu6beVl-0"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"免费商用字体","depth":2,"text":"免费商用字体"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:7.gists:font.md","_source":"content","_file":"7.gists/font.md","_stem":"7.gists/font","_extension":"md"}